The project is a website developed in PHP and MySQLi, about the sale of cakes.
Processes performed by the system, customer view:
- Customer registration to be able to buy cakes.
- Shopping cart where you can add n quantity of cakes.
- Form to add shipping address and payment method.

Processes performed by the system, administrator view:
- Add and/or delete new products.
- Increase and/or decrease the stock of the warehouse.
- Sales report by day, week or month.
- Delete registered users.

The system is implemented with: 
- Classes and abstract classes 
- Attributes and methods (public, private and protected) 
- Objects 
- Constructors in each class 
- Stored procedures
- Triggers
- JavaScript form validations
- Using Bootstrap for buttons and dynamic tables
